 ('483','Roxanne Brooks','9074556414','ak574born@yahoo.com','','Wedding Photography','1','Hello,\nIm planning on coming to DC the 5- 13 of April 2011 and am getting married on the 7th or the 8th. Im looking for a photographer and possibly an “advisor” as Im not familiar with the area.\n It is just the Bride and Groom. we are sort of eloping or having a private ceremony / vacation type thing. I want to have wedding and after wedding photos done around the monuments or suggested locations.\nI am needing pricing and any suggestions.\nThanks,\nRoxanne\n','2011-03-06 23:55:29','2011-03-06 23:55:29'),
 ('484','Kristina Buday','703-917-9444','kbuday.ga@netzero.net','June 26     1pm - 6 pm','Wedding Photography','1','would like to know pricing information','2011-03-07 10:51:01','2011-03-07 10:51:01'),
 ('485','Laura Partin','202-320-3139','lelizap@gmail.com','April 2, 2011','Wedding Photography','0','We are getting married April 2 at 3 pm in St. William\'s Chapel on the campus of Georgetown University.  It will be a Catholic ceremony (no mass, though) and the only guests will be our parents and siblings.  We\'re talking VERY low-key event.  Simple ceremony.  I\'m not even having flowers.  We are having family over to our home for a fun cook-out afterwards, so we would only need photography from 2:30 pm - 4:00 pm.  Is this something you\'d even be interested in doing?  My fiance and I may also be interested in going out to have additional photographs taken of just the two of us the next morning (maybe by the monuments, etc).  I know it\'s last-minute, but we could really use a great photographer.  Thanks!  Laura Partin  ','2011-03-07 15:20:08','2011-03-07 15:20:08'),
 ('486','Cecelia Townes','','ceceliatownes@gmail.com','October 15, 2011','Wedding Photography','0','Hello,\n\nMy fiance and I are getting married on October 15, 2011 at the Hotel Palomar in Arlington.  We would like to know your availability and information on your pricing and photograph packages.\n\nThank you,\n\nCecelia','2011-03-08 16:00:27','2011-03-08 16:00:27'),
 ('487','Samantha Barrie','917-304-0456','samanthabarrie812@gmail.com','','Wedding Photography','0','Hi!  I\'m looking for a wedding photographer for Sunday, October 23rd at The Fairfax on Embassy Row.  It\'s going to be a wedding of about 70 people with a very small bridal party.  Getting ready, the ceremony and reception will all be at The Fairfax.  Might this be something that you are able to do?  Can you tell me what your pricing would be?  Please feel free to call or email me.\nThanks!\nSamantha','2011-03-11 19:22:29','2011-03-11 19:22:29'),
 ('488','Shay Foley','919-641-7260','shaydali@hotmail.com','May 29, 2011 - 5:00-10:00?','Wedding Photography','1','My partner and I are getting married at the Donovan House in downtown DC and are looking for pricing for a few hours of shooting. \n\nThanks.\n\nShay','2011-03-11 21:12:48','2011-03-11 21:12:48'),
 ('489','Michelle Ashton','540-303-1030','shellster220@yahoo.com','6pm-8pm','Wedding Photography','1','please send me info on rates, packages, etc..\n\n49 True Apple Way #B\nInwood, WV 25428-3711\n\nTHANKS IN ADVANCE!','2011-03-12 05:17:38','2011-03-12 05:17:38'),
 ('490','Marsha Stringer','781 863-8086','stringer@mstringer.net','','Other','1','Are you Karen Sayre, formerly in Concord, MA?  If so, you photographed my daughter\'s wedding in Lexington, Oct 1999.\n\nI\'m trying to locate Bob Murray, Special Event Video Productions. We\'d like to transfer the tape to DVD, and have a copy in PAL format for family in Italy.\n\nI hope to hear from you soon.\n\nRegards,\nMarsha Stringer\nstringer@mstringer.net\nLexington, MA\n\n\n \n\n','2011-03-14 17:25:55','2011-03-14 17:25:55'),
 ('491','Eric Steinhart','847-951-1917','eric.steinhart@gmail.com','April 30, 2011','Wedding Photography','0','My fiancé and I are getting married on Saturday, April 30th, in Washington, D.C. (Cleveland Park).  We would like to hire a photographer from approximately 4:00 pm until 6:30 pm to photograph the wedding party, a brief ceremony, and a reception.  All will be at the same location.  Would you be available to photograph this event?  If so, could you please send us a cost estimate?\nMany thanks,\nEric Steinhart\neric.steinhart@gmail.com\n','2011-03-15 00:31:55','2011-03-15 00:31:55'),
 ('492','Zeina Al-Khalaf','703 6259470','zalkhala@gmu.edu','','Wedding Photography','1','.','2011-03-15 04:41:42','2011-03-15 04:41:42'),
 ('493','Maria Barhams','7652158828','mjbarhams@gmail.com','September 2012','Wedding Photography','0','If possible can you send us a pricing guide/rate sheet for your wedding services?','2011-03-15 16:58:34','2011-03-15 16:58:34'),
 ('494','Cathy Mitchell','877-322-8234','cathym@pavilionstructures.com','ASAP','Other','1','We are in need of having pictures taken of a building at the Washington Dulles International Airport once we receive permission.  Are you interested in taking this contract on?\nWe need this done as soon as I get permission.','2011-03-15 22:39:18','2011-03-15 22:39:18'),
 ('495','Brei E.','2408885198','Brei.Evans@gmail.com','anytime between 9-6pm','Other','1','Seeking temporary Assistant/internship position. Currently a student and amateur photographer seeking to learn more about the business. Hope to hear from some one soon. ','2011-03-16 04:36:24','2011-03-16 04:36:24'),
 ('496','Stephanie','9136428329','sfrieze@kc.rr.com','23rd of July 2011','Wedding Photography','1','Are you available on the 23rd of July for a wedding in the Washington DC area?\n\nThanks,\nStephanie','2011-03-18 15:56:36','2011-03-18 15:56:36'),
