 ('498','Jessie Brown ','703 907 9086','jessieivybrown@gmail.com','after 7, but email is better','Maternity Photography','0','Hi, \r\n\r\nI\'d like some information about the pricing for your maternity sessions.  I\'m amost 6 months pregnant, so I guess I\'d like to do a shoot in May or June. (I\'m due in July.) I\'m interested in an outdoor shoot - possibly with including cool DC architecture (in front of a unique door or old building, etc) and possibly some nude photos, but mostly outdoor shots. \r\nThanks!\r\nJessie','2011-03-18 20:07:29','2011-03-18 20:07:29'),
 ('499','Steven Ralston','617-529-0700','sjralston@gmail.com','Wedding 6/17/11','Wedding Photography','0','Hi --\nWe\'re a gay couple looking for a photographer for a few hours for an afternoon wedding. We will have our 2 young kids with us,  a total of 10 people or so.\nThanks,\nSteven','2011-03-19 16:26:27','2011-03-19 16:26:27'),
 ('500','Grace Jin','703-772-2296','gracesjin@gmail.com','4:00 PM-10:00 PM','Wedding Photography','1','Hello,\n\nI am interested in getting information regarding your wedding packages/rates. Please contact me at your earliest convenience. Thanks!\n\nGrace','2011-03-19 23:53:09','2011-03-19 23:53:09'),
 ('501','Matt Burke','5183318545','mattdotburke@gmail.com','October','Wedding Photography','1','Hello Eikon, we are getting married in Old Town, Alexandria in early October.  I am looking for photography quotes for a 4 hour event, about 100 people.  Thanks so much!\n\nMatt','2011-03-21 23:07:43','2011-03-21 23:07:43'),
 ('502','Robert Linares','703-987-7882','rusty.linares@yahoo.com','27 March 2011 (afternoon)','Other','1','We would like to take Engagement Photos on the National Harbor March 27, 2011. If you could please let me know if you\'re available and some cost estimates we would appreciate it. ','2011-03-22 01:05:26','2011-03-22 01:05:26'),
 ('503','Meghan Getman','716-870-0073','meghan.getman@gmail.com','4-2-11','Portraiture','0','Hi, My fiance and I live in Fort Worth TX but we will be in Washington for the Cherry Blossom Festival on April 2.  I would like to know if you are available that day to do an engagement shoot, and what the cost would be. Thanks! ~Meghan Getman\n','2011-03-22 01:46:28','2011-03-22 01:46:28');
