insert into `seo_profiles` values('1','Washington DC Photographers | Washington DC Photographer | Wedding Photographer | Maternity Photographer | Portrait Photographer | Corporate Event Photographer','washington dc photographers,washington dc photographer,washington dc wedding photographer,washington dc wedding photographers,maryland wedding photographers,virginia wedding photographers, washington dc maternity photographer,washington dc portrait photographer, washington dc corporate event photographer,eikon,eikon photographer,eikon wedding photography,eikon wedding photographer','Washington DC Photographers, Eikon Photographer is a professional wedding photographer, maternity photographer, portrait photographer, & corporate event photographer. Eikon Photographer also serves Maryland, Virginia and surrounding areas.','Washington DC Photographer | Wedding | Maternity | Portrait | Corporate Event','2009-04-29 16:16:27','2013-03-04 06:11:12','8','','aa'),
 ('2','Eikon Photographer | Washington DC Photographer | Karen Sayre','karen sayre,eikon,eikon photographer,eikon photography,washington dc photographers,washington dc photographer, washington dc wedding photographer, washington dc maternity photographer, washington dc portrait photographer,washington dc corporate events photographer,corporate events photography, maryland corporate events photographer,virginia corporate events photographer,eikon,eikon photographer,eikon corporate events photography,corporate events photography','Eikon is a professional Washington DC Photographer. Karen Sayre, Eikon Photographer provides professional photography of weddings, maternity, portraits, and corporate events. Karen Sayre also serve Maryland, Virginia and surrounding areas.','Eikon Photographer | Washington DC Photographer | Karen Sayre','2009-04-29 16:16:27','2009-05-13 11:11:05','10',null,'bb'),
 ('3','Washington DC Wedding Photographers | Washington DC Wedding Photographer','washington dc photographers,washington dc photographer,washington dc wedding photographer, washington dc wedding photographers,maryland wedding photographers,virginia wedding photographers,eikon,eikon photographer,eikon wedding photography,eikon wedding photographer','Washington DC Wedding Photographers, Washington DC Wedding Photographer, Eikon Photographer is a professional wedding photographer serving Washington DC, Maryland, Virginia and surrounding areas.','Washington DC Wedding Photographers | Washington DC Wedding Photographer','2009-04-29 20:24:01','2010-07-09 22:33:38','5','Please check out our services page for more details.\r\n*Wedding Photography*\r\n*Wedding photography prices dc* vary tremendously, so we keep it simple. \r\nWe avoid complicated *wedding photography packages*. *Our wedding photography rates* are modular, allowing for maximum flexibility in working with you wedding photography budget. To help you along download our free *wedding photography kit*. Included is a *wedding photography checklist pdf* with a *wedding photography shot list pdf*. If you need *wedding photography tips* this planning kit can really help.\r\nLooking for *gay wedding photos*? If you are having a *gay wedding dc*, we\'re currently booking many *gay weddings*. If you need information on *gay wedding venues dc*, or to find a *gay wedding officiant*, we have a *gay wedding planning checklist* to help facilitate your *gay weddings washington dc*.\r\nNot getting married in Washington dc? *Wedding photography prices in md*?\r\nOr *wedding photographer northern virginia*? We travel anywhere and everywhere.','wedding-photographer'),
 ('4','Washington DC Portrait Photographers | Washington DC Portrait Photographer','washington dc photographers,washington dc photographer,washington dc portrait photographer,portrait photography, maryland portrait photographer,virginia portrait photographer,eikon,eikon photographer,eikon portrait photography,portrait photography','Washington DC Portrait Photographers, Eikon Photographer is a professional portrait photographer serving the Washington DC, Maryland, Virginia and surrounding areas.','Washington DC Portrait Photographers | Washington DC Portrait Photographer','2009-04-29 20:29:14','2010-07-09 22:34:25','2','Please check out our services page for more details.\r\nAs a *portrait photographer washington dc *helping  clients look their very best is critical. Whether you need a picture for your website or your mother, we can guide you through every step of this sometimes intimidating process. We\'re also *portrait photographers in northern virginia * and location shoots are available in Washington DC, northern virginia and maryland.\r\n*Famly Photographers*\r\nWe are f*amily photographers*. *Family photography rates* are  typically based on a sitting fee and location. If you want *family portraits with baby* or *family portraits with pets*, we\'re open to almost anything. We will work with you to ensure a look that you\'ll be thrilled with. If you are looking for *child photographer northern virginia*, and you prefer something in your own home we can come to you.','family-photographers'),
 ('5','Washington DC Maternity Photographer | Washington DC New Born Photographer | Washington DC Maternity Photographers','washington dc photographers,washington dc photographer,washington dc maternity photographer,washington dc newborn photography, maryland maternity photographer,maryland newborn photography, virginia maternity photographer,virginia newborn photography,eikon,eikon photographer','Washington DC Maternity Photographers, Eikon Photographer is a professional maternity photographer, newborn photographer serving Washington DC, Maryland, Virginia and surrounding areas.','Washington DC Maternity Photographer | Newborn Photographer','2009-04-29 20:31:13','2010-07-09 22:35:14','6','Please check out our services page for more details.\r\n*Maternity Photography*\r\n*Pregnancy Photography*\r\nAs *artistic women photographers* we understand the importance of *maternity photo sessions*. *Maternity portraits* are a spectacular way to capture the beauty of this awesome moment in a woman\'s life. \r\n*Pregnancy photography prices*. \r\n*Maternity photo prices* depend on whether you choose a single or multiple session package. Although these are typically done in our Washington DC photo studio, in home is also an option. *Pregnancy photography with children* or spouse is very popular, and single sessions can be rolled over into newborn photography packages and also i*nfant photography*.  Why travel to dc?  Whilst there are *maternity photographers in maryland *and *maternity portrait studios in maryland* your *professional maternity shoot *should reflect your artistic taste rather than where you live necessarily. The same applies if you need *maternity photography northern va*. We can help translate your vision into reality.\r\n\r\n*Newborn Photography*\r\n*Infant Photography*\r\nIf you are looking for the best *baby photographer washington dc*, look no further.\r\nI love them all... and have so much fun with them regardless of their age!!\r\nGetting out of the house can seem a huge struggle during those first initial weeks with your newborn. As *professional newborn photographers*, we provide a soothing setting with no rushing. Take time out to feed and cuddle. These newborn photos are spectacular!\r\n\r\n*Infant photo shoot.*\r\nI\'ve been a *newborn photographer washington dc* for over 10 years and I\'ve found that calm, playful and fun are key ingredients along with a generous time schedule!!\r\nInfants are fun on their own of course, but we can also add mom into the picture too for a wonderful *mother and child photo shoot*.\r\nOne frequently asked question is a which points to schedule your baby photography. Although timing is entirely up to you, here\'s the most often chosen timing.\r\n*baby photography newborn*\r\n*baby photography 3 months*\r\n*baby photography 4 months*\r\n*baby photography 6 months*\r\nIf you are looking for *baby photographer northern virginia*, or *baby photographer maryland* ........ we can help, either in our studio or in your home.','maternity-photography'),
 ('6','Washington DC Corporate Events Photographers | Washington DC Corporate Events Photographer','washington dc photographers,washington dc photographer,washington dc corporate events photographer,corporate events photography, maryland corporate events photographer,virginia corporate events photographer,eikon,eikon photographer,eikon corporate events photography,corporate events photography','Washington DC Corporate Events Photographers, Washington DC Corporate Events Photographer, Eikon Photographer is a professional corporate events photographer serving Washington DC, Maryland, Virginia and surrounding areas.','Washington DC Corporate Events Photographers | Corporate Events Photographer','2009-04-29 20:32:36','2010-07-09 22:35:55','7','Boudoir  photography refers to images that have themes of romance, sensuality, and flirtation. It is not necessary to be nude or revealing in female boudoir pictures. It has more to do with an attitude or state of mind than the state of dress or undress. The primary ideas conveyed in female boudoir portrait are love, affection, romance, and giving. Female Boudoir Photography is almost always done in the studio.Lawrence uses subtle lighting, sensual  poses, and a comfortable  studio atmosphere to help put you at ease and to bring out that sexy you. Female boudoir photos are the perfect gift for your significant other, boyfriend, girlfriend, lover, or the groom on your wedding day. Boudoir photography brings out the natural beauty all women possess. You can order  portfolio albums,  calendars, and wall portraits as a gift for a birthday, your anniversary, Sweetest Day, Valentine\'s Day, Christmas, Father\'s Day, or just as a romantic surprise.\r\nGlamour  Photography is a term commonly used to describe a flattering type of photograph usually taken of one person. Glamour means SEXY - posing in a sexy manner or wearing low-cut or transparent blouses, short skirts, open shorts and/or shirts, or some topless.  Glamour Photography can also be suggestive but non-revealing.\r\nA Glamour Photographic Session takes approximately one to three hours to complete. The challenge in Glamour Photography is to employ minimal garments effectively to create a visually pleasing, thematically intriguing image. In simple terms, Glamour Photography is all about the model, not her clothes. Less clothing means MORE model.Lawrence uses his resources and creativity to create a  classy and romantic piece of art that ignites confidence and excitement in a  bride or wife, re-enforces beauty in a woman, and romance in a couple.\r\nWe specialize in photographing the essence and beauty of  every woman. Our clients are diverse and range from mothers to soon to be  brides. Our goal is to celebrate each woman individually, capturing her in a  new light that can re-ignite confidence and the way she sees herself.\r\nWe provide boudoir and glamour photography in the *washington dc area*. This includes *professional photographers northern virginia*, *photography alexandria va, photographers arlington va* and bethesda md area\r\nWe work extensively around the dc area, including northern virginia, arlington va, alexandria va','photographer-dc'),
